<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">杕杜</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson80edae939665">
<p>有杕之杜，其叶湑湑。独行踽踽。岂无他人？不如我同父。嗟行之人，胡不比焉？人无兄弟，胡不佽焉？<br />有杕之杜，其叶菁菁。独行睘睘。岂无他人？不如我同姓。嗟行之人，胡不比焉？人无兄弟，胡不佽焉？</p>
</div>
</div>
