<a id="dingsx36706" href="javascript:dingsx('36706','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=80edae939665')">有用(1)</a><a id="paisx36706" style=" margin-left:10px;" href="javascript:paisx('36706','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=80edae939665')">没用(0)</a>
</div>
